text.autoconfig.bettermineshafts-fabric-: YUNG's Better Mineshafts
Main Settings
Spawn Rates & More
Ore Deposits
Mineshaft Spawn Rate
Minimum y-coordinate
The lowest the floor of a mineshaft can be.
If you set this too low the mineshafts will get burned by lava!
Maximum y-coordinate
The highest the floor of a mineshaft can be.
Spawn Rates & More
Customize spawn rates for various mineshaft parts and decorations.
Ore Deposits
Configure ore deposit spawn chances.
MAKE SURE ALL THE VALUES ADD UP TO 100,
or things won't work the way you want them to!!
Lantern Spawn Rate
The spawn rate for lanterns in the main shaft.
Torch Spawn Rate
The spawn rate for torches in small shafts.
Workstation Spawn Rate
The spawn rate for workstation side rooms along the main shaft.
Workstation Cellar Spawn Rate
The spawn rate for workstation cellars below workstations along the main shaft.
Small Shaft Spawn Rate
The spawn rate for smaller tunnels that generate along the main shaft.
Cobweb Spawn Rate
The spawn rate for cobwebs.
Small Shaft Chest Minecart Spawn Rate
The spawn rate for minecarts holding chests in small shafts.
Main Shaft Chest Minecart Spawn Rate
The spawn rate for minecarts holding chests in the main shaft.
Small Shaft TNT Minecart Spawn Rate
The spawn rate for minecarts holding TNT in small shafts.
Main Shaft TNT  Minecart Spawn Rate
The spawn rate for minecarts holding TNT in the main shaft.
Abandoned Miners' Outpost Spawn Rate
Percent chance of an Abandoned Miners' Outpost to spawn
at the end of a small mineshaft tunnel.
Small Shaft Piece Chain Length
The number of "pieces" (e.g. straight, turn, etc) in a single small shaft.
This determines the overall size of small shafts.
Enable Ore Deposits
Cobble Spawn Chance (Empty deposit)
Percent chance of an ore deposit being cobblestone only.
Coal Spawn Chance
Percent chance of an ore deposit containing coal.
Iron Spawn Chance
Percent chance of an ore deposit containing iron.
Redstone Spawn Chance
Percent chance of an ore deposit containing redstone.
Gold Spawn Chance
Percent chance of an ore deposit containing gold.
Lapis Spawn Chance
Percent chance of an ore deposit containing lapis.
Emerald Spawn Chance
Percent chance of an ore deposit containing emerald.
Diamond Spawn Chance
Percent chance of an ore deposit containing diamond.
